#: ../../S/stomp-on.rst:5
msgid "stomp on"
msgstr "stomp on"

#: ../../S/stomp-on.rst:7
msgid "vt\\."
msgstr "他動詞"

#: ../../S/stomp-on.rst:9
msgid ""
"To inadvertently overwrite something important, usually automatically. \"All"
" the work I did this weekend got stomped on last night by the nightly server"
" script.\" Compare :ref:`scribble`\\, :ref:`mangle`\\, :ref:`trash`\\, "
":ref:`scrog`\\, :ref:`roach`\\."
msgstr ""
"たいてい自動的に、重要な何かをうっかり上書きすること。「この週末にやった作業が全部、昨夜の夜間サーバースクリプトにstomp onされた。」\\ "
":ref:`scribble`\\ 、\\ :ref:`mangle`\\ 、\\ :ref:`trash`\\ 、\\ :ref:`scrog`\\ "
"、\\ :ref:`roach`\\ と比較せよ。"
